high_descs: Turn right and head straight ahead to the fridge.
Remove the red cloth from the fridge.
Turn around and go down the path a bit, then walk around the counters to the left to get to the sink.
Rinse off the cloth in the sink and pick it back up.
Go around the counters and stand where the counters next to the sink meet the wall.
Place the cloth down on the counter just next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a cloth with water in a sink and place that cloth on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, take the cloth from the rack, close the fridge.
Turn around, move straight, turn right, move towards the sink back side.
Put the cloth inside the sink, wash it, take back the cloth.
Turn right, and left, take left towards the counter top.
Put the cloth on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: To take the cloth from fridge, wash it in the sink, put it on the counter top.

high_descs: Pick the cloth from the fridge.
Turn right and turn right towards the sink.
Turn right and put the cloth inside the sink.
Rinse it off, and turn left to the countertop.
Place the cloth on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place the cloth on the countertop.
